{
  "stem": "2074.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway, I tried to tell the guy who I am, what I am.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sat all day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then for the night, they want to go around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They're spies, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they want to leave me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm going with you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, you're going to get killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I says, I'm gonna get killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'd rather be killed that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had nothing to live for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I want to be killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's against the Russian law.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We are spies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We're not supposed to have you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I says, put me in as another spy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I am going with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took me down to the house, to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Manka. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Manka ?] gave us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tried to give me a pair of shoes or whatever to wear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went for the night with the soldiers crawling around all under the German front lines, all on the people that living there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We happened to go to that place that I knew they were hiding us before, where I jumped off the roof.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all on that borderline.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We crawled around all night long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went back to a suburb of Horochow called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the civilians were evacuated because the front line was establishing right in that place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And lucky for me that I left with those soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would-- they evacuated the rest of the people, and I could have died in that hole, sitting there by myself, because they couldn't take me with them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they told me that-- that now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we come into a city, to a-- to a house, and they want to have breakfast.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody-- the people left the cows and they left the chickens.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
